      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 4,
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1) is developed under ISO 9001-certified quality management with full V&V test suite documentation. Internal SQA audit confirms compliance with ASME V&V 10-2006 software quality requirements. Version-controlled source, regression test coverage >95%, and traceability matrix between requirements and test cases are on file.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
