        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "description": "Solver must be developed under a documented quality management system with traceable V&V test suite achieving ≥90% coverage of relevant physics modules. All defect reports affecting hemolysis-relevant numerics must be resolved or formally accepted."
