      "rationale": "Simulation setup was independently reviewed by a second qualified CFD analyst following a documented review checklist (CHECKLIST-CFD-VAD-2024). Boundary condition assignments, material property inputs, turbulence model selection, and hemolysis model parameters were each verified against the simulation plan. Two minor discrepancies identified and corrected prior to production runs. No use errors remain in the archived simulation files.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
