      "rationale": "Experimental hemolysis measurements performed on three independently manufactured pump specimens (serial numbers P-001, P-002, P-003) drawn from the same production batch. Each specimen tested in triplicate at each operating point (n=45 total test runs). Inter-specimen variability (CV 4.2%) and intra-specimen repeatability (CV 1.8%) are both documented. Sample size provides 90% statistical power to detect a 10% difference in NIH at α=0.05.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
        "id": "https://uofa.net/morrison/ac/test-samples",
        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "description": "At least three independently manufactured specimens must be tested. Replicate measurements must be performed to characterize both inter-specimen and intra-specimen variability. Statistical power analysis must confirm adequacy of sample size for the intended comparison."
      }
